parameters:
Mercenary: "Since the Demon Lord was defeated, a lot of
mercenaries from various bases have been getting laid
off..."

Mercenary: "And those people, they're starting to work as
mercenaries for bad organizations just for the money..."

"It's been five days, huh. How's it going? Making good
progress?"
"Yeah, I've managed to complete the blueprint at least."

"No, not at all. For now, I'm just gathering information
about the human trafficking organization..."

"If we rush and get found out by the enemy, it will only
make them harder to find."

"With Tina Onee-san and Selphie-san not here, we need to
ensure our own safety while steadily moving forward."

"So? You called me here today because we're going to gather
materials, right?"

"Yeah, actually there's a special ore that forms on the back
of a monster called Gugukasit's called Lucent Glass ore."

"I absolutely need that ore for the equipment creation, so I
want you to come with me to collect it."
"In the depths of the Eld Cavern."

"The ecosystem of the nearby monsters has changed, but
Gugukas are protected by hard ore and live in cold places,
so..."
"I'm pretty sure it's still in the back."
"Got it. If that's the case, let's head out right away."

"The deeper parts of the Eld Cavern are home to even
stronger monsters, so don't let your guard down."

"Leave it to me. If it comes to combat, I'll send even high-
level monsters flying."

Villager: "I heard they made the dick on this statue bigger
than it actually is."
Villager: "I wonder how big it really is..."
Guard: "Beyond this point lies the nobility district."

Guard: "To prevent crimes targeting nobles, we ask those
without a permit to refrain from passing through."
Guard: "You will need a pass to proceed from here."

Tina: "Yes, here it is. I've come on a request from the
noble Maroges."

Guard: "Indeed, I have confirmed it, Lord Maroges. I will
guide you."
Guard: "Beyond here lies the Noble Quarter."

Guard: "To prevent crimes targeting nobles, we ask those
without a permit to refrain from passing through."

Maintenance Worker: "Recently, the deterioration of this
wall has been progressing."

Maintenance Worker: "We're currently doing repair work, so
please wait a while before passing through here."
Guard: "Beyond this point lies the noble district."

Guard: "To prevent crimes targeting nobles, we ask those
without a permit to refrain from passing through."
Guard: "You need a pass to get through here."

Tina: "Yes, here it is. I've come on a request from the
noble Maroges."

Guard: "Indeed, I have confirmed it. You are Maroges-sama. I
will show you the way."
Guard: "Beyond here lies the noble district."

Guard: "To prevent crimes targeting nobles, we ask those
